   &lt;td style="text-align:left;min-width: 4cm; border-left:1px solid;background-color: ##5ca4a9 !important;"&gt; How unequal is the level of education achieved by the population aged 15 years older? &lt;/td&gt;
   &lt;td style="text-align:left;min-width: 4cm; border-left:1px solid;background-color: ##5ca4a9 !important;"&gt;  &lt;/td&gt;
  &lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

